p0166 = "At the third answer the Bishop once again lifts the holy Relics from the table and makes the sign of the Cross with them three times on the closed doors. And as soon as the third answer is completed, he pushes the closed doors. When they have been opened, the Bishop enters the Church, with the Clergy and the Singers, and with them the whole People, as the Apolytikion is chanted."
