p0193 = "Lord God, our Saviour, who do and direct all things for the salvation of the human race, accept the entreaties of your unworthy servants for them to perform without condemnation the Dedication of this Church, that has been built for our salvation and the praise of your glory, in the name of Saint N., and to make the installation of the Table in it."
