p0277 = "Alleluia!"
p0278 = "and he makes three Crosses with it, one in the middle and two on either side. And having handed back the vessel, with his hand he wipes the whole of the holy Table with the three Crosses. He also makes Crosses with it on the column. While this is being done the following is chanted."
